{"word":"ἐφοδεύω","slug":"ἐφοδεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐφοδεύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἔφοδος</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to visit, go the rounds, patrol</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἐφοδεύεται</el> <i>the rounds are made</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <i>to watch over</i>, <el>ἀγῶσιν</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}